Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of image processing techniques to outline the fortified artificial hills and trenches surrounding them, which suggests that it falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) categories. Additionally, the use of satellite images and edge detection techniques could also place it under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer security (cs.CR) categories. Finally, the mention of the symbolic meaning behind the planning of the fortresses could potentially place it under the augmented reality (cs.AR) category.
